data.description: Ready for Immediate Move-In! Welcome to an abode of serenity and elegance - the ''Lilac'' floor plan! This ready-to-move-in property blends style with convenience, designed to complement a modern lifestyle. With 4 generously-sized bedrooms, 2 plush baths, and a 2-car garage, you have all the room to grow and create lasting memories. The house welcomes you with an open great room and dining area that radiates warmth and friendliness, certainly your go-to spot for cozy entertainment or festive gatherings. Adjacent to this space is the gourmet kitchen, a dream for culinary enthusiasts!
